I '''James B. Patterson''' (mibait Marzo 22, 1947) metung yang is an Americanung [[talasulat]] da reng [[nobelan]]ng [[thriller (genre)|thriller]], a kilalang dili uling king kayang serie tungkul king piksyonal a psikologong i [[Alex Cross]], king ''[[Alex Cross (serieng nobela)|Alex Cross series]]''. Sinulat no muring Patterson deng serieng Michael Bennett, ''[[Women's Murder Club]]'', ''[[Maximum Ride]]'', ''[[Daniel X]]'', ampo ing serieng ''[[Witch and Wizard]]'', ampong dakal a thriller a e kayabe king serie, ampo kareng librung e piksyon (''nonfiction'') ampong nobelang  romance.
His books have sold more than 270 million copies.

